&lt;p&gt;You cannot pass variable values from the current page JavaScript code to the current page PHP code... PHP code runs at the server side, and it doesn&apos;t know anything about what is going on on the client side.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You need to pass variables to PHP code from the HTML form using another mechanism, such as submitting the form using the GET or POST methods.&lt;/p&gt;

